      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SO YOU ASSUME (2) continued his winning form with another strong run after leading to make it two on end, scoring by 2 lengths (27.81) at this track over 485m. Some good form is emerging from his last run. Expected to go well again. RIVERSDALE MICK (3) stuck on well last time to finish 2 lengths back in second (23.14) at this track in a Free For All over 410m. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Can feature again. HATARI (6) had been going along well winning a Grade 5 H three back then placing at The Meadows before missing the frame latest when eighth (30.29) at Sandown. Can turn it around this time. PAW MISSY (4) is a last-start placegetter after leading early on – sure to have admirers.",
